export default `<body class="view" contenteditable="true" spellcheck="true" style="overflow-y: hidden; cursor: text; height: 5233px;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">组织者手册</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">一、</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">故事背景：</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">朔阳关外的老槐树村，蓝天如洗，山峦叠障。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">村子里的打谷场上，几个小童在追逐嬉戏。嘴里念唱着不知名的歌谣：槐叶光,粮空仓,</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">槐籽秃,亲人哭, 槐花落，黄泉祸，槐树枯，鬼幡升。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">小儿无知，不知道歌谣的意思，而打谷场里的大人们却心知肚明。这一切都要从今年开春的村民大会说起。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">门前有槐，百鬼夜行。但在几个月前的老槐树村却并不是这样。村口的那棵老槐树是许多人心中的守护神，人们春天闻着槐花香，夏天乘着槐树荫，秋冬喝着高梁酒槐花酿，日子过得别提多舒坦。可是自从今年开春，村长吴富贵在村民大会上带头要砍树修路之后，便不知从何处传来这首歌谣，老槐树村变得人心惶惶。大家纷纷传言，老槐树是村里的守护神，砍了树，必然会有血光之灾。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">离奇的是，接下来的三个月里，村里接二连三地发生怪事。先是周家老大周琦众目暌暌地从自家屋顶上跳了下来；再是公社干事季礼全在从城里回村的拖拉机上突然发疯，跳车坠入山崖；一个月前村里的傻子傻柱在自家院子里突然暴毙；接着住在村东头的刘金山和杀猪的牛二民发生口角，一起掉进河里淹死了；七天前，村里的水儿姑娘跳了后山的风蚀崖。这些人本来没什么共同点，要非说有，就是在开春的村民大会上投了砍树的票。砍树者死的诅咒，像刀子一样刺痛每个村民的心灵。整个老槐树村陷入一种恐惧的死寂中，再也没有了往日的欢乐…………二、涉案人员：</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">终石明： 19岁，三个月前从北京来老槐树村插队的知青； （不推荐新手玩）赤脚医生： 63岁，（实际上19岁）走街串巷的行医者；（不推荐新手玩）赵香兰： 30岁，风韵犹存的寡妇；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">秀琴: 38岁,村长媳妇;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">郭大槐： 18岁，槐花树下长大的少年；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">钱有钱： 35岁，两天前来到老槐树村的有钱人； （不推荐新手玩）本案死者：45岁，老槐树村村长吴富贵；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">三、游戏流程：</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第一环节：选择角色—阅读剧本（本环节中参与者可一次性阅读剧本的全部章节，其中包括故事背景、身份介绍、角色定位、昨天的事、今天的事、你已知的其他人、你的秘密等）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第二环节：玩家自我介绍—微型剧目演绎（修路动员大会）—案发前后时间线简单梳理（本环节中玩家为了隐藏自己的秘密，可以在时间线上有所隐瞒）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第三环节：第一轮取证。每位玩家可以取走3条线索。（线索卡需要按照顺序被取走，第一轮只开放私人区域的前两条线索和公共区域（包括办公室和打谷场）的前三条线索—同时玩家一对一私聊（玩家每取得一条线索需要花费1点体力值，本轮取证中每位玩家至多可以搜取3条线索。）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第四环节：第一轮公开讨论。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第五环节：第二轮取证—同时玩家一对一私聊。（本轮开放全部区域的后三条线索，线索卡需要按照顺序被取走，本轮取证中每位玩家可以搜取4条线索。）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第六环节：第二轮公开讨论。（此环节中组织者应提醒玩家注意组织者手册第四部分的注意事项）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第七环节：票选凶手。（玩家每人一票，如果出现平票则由玩家共同再次确</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">定票选对象）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第八环节：玩家共同回答以下几个问题，如果回答正确或是经过全部玩家同意，则可以结案。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">1死者是谁（需回答姓名，年龄）2死者为什么会在这里</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">3死者砍树的真正原因是什么4终石明是谁</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">5寡妇和秀琴八岁时救起的女婴分别是谁6老槐树村为什么会消失</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">四、注意事项：</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">1本游戏中，凶手可以在任何事情上说谎，而其他玩家可以在与自己的秘密有关的事情上做隐瞒，但组织者需要提醒其他玩家，在相当多的情况下，普通玩家说谎不利于案件的明晰。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2在第二轮讨论之前可以询问玩家是否需要尸检报告。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">尸检报告：尸体右脸有不规则裂创；脑后遭受打击，有轻微颅内出血，可致短暂休克；四肢和背部有广泛软组织、肌肉挫伤；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">死因：溺水引起的机械性室息伴随呼吸功能衰竭</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">3第二轮私聊结束之后，组织者应提醒玩家死者脸上带着的人皮面具因为泡水而变形，询问玩家是否揭开死者的人皮面具。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">人皮面具下面的人脸：与钱有钱长得一样，只是略微苍老一点。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">4 【石头手札】内容： （根据游戏难度分为简单版和复杂版，可由玩家自行选择）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">简单版：</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">说出来你可能不会相信，我在老槐树村经历了人生中最为离奇的一件事。1959年4月15日，我得知吴富贵和几个村民要放火烧死崔家三口，于是动了恻隐之心，便在火里救下了崔家的小儿子小九，当我和崔小九一起跑到村口那棵老槐树下的时候，离奇的事情发生了，我们俩一起晕了过去，再醒来时还是在老槐树下。天已经大亮，可是奇怪的是老槐树村的村民都不认识我们了。我几番打听，终于得知了真相，原来我们不知道为什么竟然来到了1949年的老槐树村，得知这个事实之后我惊恐极了，久久不能平复，很想弄清楚到底发生了什么。但看到年纪还小的小九，还是决定先把他安顿好。于是，我把小九带回了北京，让他随了我的姓取名佟石明。回到北京之后，我积极申请去老槐树村插队，终于在1958年，我得到了革委会的批准来到老槐树村。不管怎么样，我一定要搞清楚1959年的4月15日到底发生了什么事情，为什么我会如此离奇地回到十年前…………1959年6月</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">复杂版：</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">1959年我在老槐树村插队的时候经历了一件不可思议的事情，4月15日，我在大火中救了一个孩子，奇怪的是我和这个孩子一起逃到老槐树下之后却回到了1949年…………</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">5【郭氏族训】木神姜无，战恶兽于朔阳，斩恶兽于梦潔。伤而不治，藏于此地，化为槐树，可司瞬息之变化，可掌时空之秩序。吾郭氏子弟，世代守护姜无，树在人在，树死人亡。如有违誓约，万死莫辞。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">6第二轮公开讨论时，组织者应提醒玩家，赵香兰拥有一份澳敌隆使用说明，并询问赵香兰是否开启；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">澳敌隆：高毒杀鼠剂。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">慢性药：鼠类服用后2—3小时发生作用。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">特点：抗凝血作用缓慢，不易引起鼠类警觉，容易歼灭害鼠。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">7当大家发现死者为钱有钱时，应提醒玩家，村长夫人秀琴有【招魂】技能，询问秀琴是否为死者招魂；如果启动技能则转向注意事项8；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">8招魂技能开启时，死者亡灵自白：（根据游戏难度可由玩家选择简单版还是复杂版）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">亡灵自白简单版：</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">我是阿有，是老槐树村郝家大爷的儿子，我从小在外工作，1969年7月13日，我想回到村子接父亲去城里生活，但是来到记忆中的老槐树村，这里除了一棵老槐树什么都没有，我在原地找了好几天，依然什么也没找到，于是就回到了城里。后来我听说就在我到达村子的前一天，老槐树村的村舍和村民竟然一夕之间都消失了。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">光阴似箭，转眼就到了1979年，我在一份报纸上得知，十年前的老槐树村是因为被陨石击中，所以整个村子才突然消失了。而陨石之所以会击中村子，是因为村口那棵老槐树磁场巨大，与陨石的碎片发生了牵引。7月15日，我回到老槐树村的原址，想在老槐树下祭拜一下父亲。但却不知道什么原因，被一道白光刺中眼睛昏了过去，再醒来的时候，我已经来到了1969年7月10日的老槐树村，我知道两天之后就是陨石毁灭村子的日子，想到报纸上说陨石是因为老槐树强大的磁场才击中村子，我觉得，能救自己唯一的办法也许就是毁掉这棵树。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">在村子里的包打听那里，我得知了村长吴富贵十年前已经将我爹逼死，后来还一直在假冒我爹给我寄信，于是我趁夜里杀了吴富贵，然后我在赤脚医生那里偷了可以做人皮面具的东西，拓着吴富贵的脸，做了一张假脸。因为我知道，只有拥有了村长的权力，砍树才有可能实现。我几次三番地尝试去砍过老槐树，可都被郭大槐制止了。7月12日这一天终于到了，可是陨石却没有如期落下，我</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">想也许是报道的时间出了差错，为了以防万一我还是利用村长的身份加紧砍树的进程。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">昨天夜里，我在吴富贵的抽屈里找到了一个备忘录，里面记录了寡妇赵香兰杀人的罪证，我想到可以利用这个威胁赵香兰支持砍树。但是今天中午我和赵香兰争执的时候，不知道被谁打晕了，后来我再醒过来，就发现我被绑住四肢，塞上手帕，拖进了井里。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">亡灵自白复杂版：</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">我叫阿有， 1979年我看到一份报纸得知父亲十年前在一场灾难中丧生，于是我回到父亲丧生的地方想要祭拜他，但却不知为何回到了1969年，我为了阻止自己也在灾难中丧生于是杀了村长吴富贵想要取代他做一些事情，但是还没有做到这件事情的时候，我就被杀了…………</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">【真相】</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">前言：</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">战国时期的大将姜无，骁勇善战，死后被封为木神。木神降妖除魔庇佑苍生，500年前战恶兽于朔阳，斩恶兽于梦潔。但自己却伤而不治，化为一株木灵，成了老槐树村口的那棵老槐树。也许由于姜无生前可司瞬息之变化，可掌时空之秩序，这棵老槐树也变成了一个可以跨越时空的介质。但是也因为老槐树强大的磁场，1969年7月12日，一颗硕大的陨石砸中了老槐树村，幸有姜无的庇佑，老槐树村没有村毁人亡，而是被砸进了平行时空中。虽然在外人看来老槐树村好像从地球上消失了一样，但村里的人们却一直过着太阳照常升起的生活…………</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">案情梳理:</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">十年前的一天，村长吴富贵偶然间得知住在村东的郝大爷有一个在东北工作的儿子阿有，阿有经常通过公社给老槐树村的父亲寄钱，吴富贵一直很想得到这笔钱。适逢住在郝大爷隔壁的崔家三口得了疫病，吴富贵不敢明目张胆地害郝大爷，于是就逼迫郝大爷去给生病的崔家人送饭，果然没过多久郝大爷就染上疫病死了。于是吴富贵模仿郝大爷的笔迹继续和郝大爷的儿子阿有联系，如愿得到阿有寄给他爹郝大爷的钱。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">崔家三口的疫病越发严重，吴富贵的媳妇秀琴出主意让吴富贵放火烧了崔家杜绝瘟疫。可是崔家的9岁的儿子崔小九却被村里善良的知青小石头救下，小石头和崔小九一起通过老槐树回到了1949年，小石头给9岁的崔小九取名为终石明。光阴似箭，九年后，小石头因为想弄清楚当年的缘何，只身来到老槐树村插队，1959年4月15日，小石头在调查事情真相的时候在大火中丧生，吴富贵等人在崔家找到三具尸骨认定崔家三口已死。与吴富贵一起放火的周琦等人联名推举吴富贵为村长，“崔家三口”的尸骨被藏在崔家后院，瘟疫中死去的郝大爷</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">也被葬在了崔家，崔家成了村里的禁地。同时，1959年4月15日小石头丧生当天，佟石明也追随哥哥的脚步来到村里，并在大火中救下了一个名叫崔小九的9岁男孩，佟石明送走了崔小九，想返回村子找自己的哥哥石头，却在途径老槐树下的时候又一次穿越，来到1969年4月的老槐树村，被当成前来插队的知青，佟石明不知自己已经到了1969年的老槐树村，还依然认为自己活在1959年刚来老槐树村找哥哥的时候。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">1969年，长大后的崔小九习医归来，想要找到当年纵火的村民报仇，崔小九将裸头草碱的粉末下在周琦、季礼全、刘金山、牛二民以及秀琴的饭食或药物里，前四个人都中毒而死，秀琴因为和水儿拿错了药而逃过一劫，而水儿却死于非命。佟石明在知青的三个月里与水儿一见钟情，深爱水儿的终石明探查水儿死因，得知水儿长期受村长吴富贵欺负，准备杀了吴富贵替水儿报仇。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">村长媳妇秀琴嗜赌如命，欠下300元高利贷，又偶然间得知村干部因公殉职可以得到300元抚恤金，于是动了杀机想要杀死吴富贵骗取抚恤金。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">吴富贵长久以来一直觊觎老槐树村郭家的槐花酿，甚至想国积一大批槐花酿，然后砍了村口的老槐树卖绝版，狠捞一笔。这件事被郭家独子郭大槐得知，再加上郭爷爷遗嘱：树在人在，树死人亡。于是便引起了郭大槐的杀机。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">寡妇赵香兰，从小被白水村一户姓赵的人家收养，赵香兰8岁的时候（1947年），来老槐树村串门，在梦潔河上捡了一个竹篮，里面有个女婴，赵香兰把女婴救回来，放在老槐树下乘凉，自己去喊大人们。女婴通过老槐树回到了八年前（1939年），这时8岁的村长媳妇秀琴在老槐树下捡了女婴想带回家养。但女婴却被白水村一户姓赵的人家带回去收养了（就是后来的赵香兰）。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">1969年7月13日35岁的郝有钱（阿有）想回到老槐树村接自己的父亲去城里，但是却发现老槐树村一夕之前消失的事情，探寻无果郝有钱回到了城里。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">日月如梭，转眼到了1979年的一天，45岁的郝有钱在报纸上看到10年前老槐树村消失的原因是因为被陨石击中村落。认为父亲应该和其他村民都在陨石毁村时丧生。1979年7月15日，45岁的郝有钱回到老槐树下祭拜父亲郝大爷，却在老槐树下不经意间穿越回了1969年7月10日的老槐树村，45岁的郝有钱知道陨石即将坠落，想要逃走却发现村子四周无路可逃，于是想砍掉老槐树来阻止村毁人亡。45岁的郝有钱从包打听处得知吴富贵害死了自己的父亲，于是杀了吴富贵假扮村长来以求利用村长的权力砍掉老槐树。但最终还是由于郭大槐的多次阻止，没有成功砍树。7月12日陨石落下，老槐树村被砸进平行世界，而村子里的人们并没有察觉到异象。但45岁的郝有钱认为也许是陨石坠落时间报道有误，仍不肯放松，还是一意坚持砍树。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">又到了1969年7月13日， 35岁的郝有钱想回到老槐树村接自己的父亲去城里，但是却发现老槐树村不见了，只留下了那棵风霜古朴的老槐树，摸着村口的老槐树，35岁的郝有钱穿越到了平行时空中1969年7月13日的老槐树村，并在包打听处得知父亲被吴富贵害死的真相，决定找“吴富贵”报仇。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">1969年阴历7月14日，知青佟石明在村里唱夜戏的时候，利用小孔成像制造鬼影装神弄鬼，想让大家认为村长‘吴富贵’要被鬼差勾魂。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">1969年阴历7月15日（中元节）早晨9点左右，知青终石明拿着鱼线去公社找‘吴富贵’想要勒死他并做出鬼差锁魂的假象，但是没有找到吴富贵，却在公社撞见来买老鼠药的秀琴。中午12点，秀琴给‘吴富贵’的饭菜里下了老鼠药之后，遇到来催债的高利贷，因此躲进了隔壁寡妇赵香兰的柴房。而寡妇赵香兰当时被‘吴富贵”叫去打谷场，吴富贵欲威胁赵香兰支持砍树，正好祭奠水儿后下山的知青佟石明路过听到有动静，于是用弹弓打了‘吴富贵’救下了寡妇赵香兰。1点半，钱老板去郭大槐家谈事，路过打谷场，看到自己的仇人躺在打谷</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">场上，杀意立起。钱老板用吊着水桶的麻绳绑住‘吴富贵”，又把寡妇掉在地上的手帕塞进‘吴富贵’嘴里，然后将吴富贵拖进井里。途中因为‘吴富贵’挣扎，钱老板打了‘吴富贵’一拳，在‘吴富贵’的右脸上留下了淤肿（钱是左撇子，因此左手打的是死者的右脸）。接着钱老板就去了郭大槐家里，找郭大槐谈槐花酿的事情。钱老板走后，寡妇赵香兰和知青终石明先后回到打谷场找自己遗落的手帕和弹弓，都未找到。2点10分左右，赤脚医生（崔小九）来到打谷场，把裸头草碱的粉末下在了‘吴富贵’的演讲稿上。但是‘吴富贵’此时已经被钱老板杀死在打谷场的井里…………</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">线索说明：</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">1赤脚医生</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">①白色粉末，裸头草碱晒干磨成的粉末；（裸头草碱的粉末，指向赤脚医生杀害周琦等人）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">②人皮面具; (指向崔小九假扮老者的事实)</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">③一块手表，是终石明救了崔小九时给他的手表；（指向终石明救了崔小九）④医书，上面记载着裸头草碱可致幻；（指向周琦等人死前发疯的原因）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">⑤一首打油诗，其实是死亡名单；（字谜，指向周琦等人是被赤脚医生杀死</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">的）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">欲求风调叹无言（周）撇下老李度春秋（季）文笔似刀汉家臣（刘）一生别离为耕耘（牛）今有二王堂上坐（琴）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">问心自可上苍穹(吴) 2 知青佟石明</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">① 一块石头挂坠； （指向知青小石头）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">② 1959年4月从北京到老槐树村的火车票； （证明知青是从1959年穿越到</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">1969年的）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">③水儿的日记本，上面提到自己被吴富贵欺负； （指向知青的杀人动机）④ 一串用鱼线倒着穿起来的蘑菇；（指向知青制造鬼影装神弄鬼）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">⑤一些用来做木工的道具； （指向知青的弹弓和中空木板）3寡妇赵香兰</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">①</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">赵香兰的心情日记本；（指向6月15日杀害傻柱和6月18被村长威胁）② 一件黑布衫中间裹着把小刀；（指向赵香兰想杀吴富贵）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">③ 你扎的小人，上面的名字是吴富贵；（指向赵香兰痛恨吴富贵）④ 你院子里石碾上的血迹； （指向赵香兰杀傻柱）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">一个蓝色的荷包； （指向赵香兰就是当年那个女婴）4 村长媳妇秀琴</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">①一桌丰盛的午餐，桌下有几只死老鼠； （指向秀琴下毒害吴富贵）②村干部抚恤条例； （300元）（指向秀琴想得到抚恤金的杀机）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">③</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">高利贷借款的单据； （300元）（与300元抚恤金联系起来）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">④一份1979年的报纸； （指向45岁的郝有钱假扮的吴富贵是从1979年穿</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">越来的，以及郝有钱一定要砍掉老槐树的原因一避免村子被陨石击中）⑤吴富贵酒窖里多罐槐花酿； （指向郭大槐的杀机和真吴富贵砍树的真正原</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">因）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">5 郭大槐</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">①两张槐花酿秘方，其中一张为复刻版；（指向吴富贵偷秘方和郭大槐杀机）② 许多份手抄的老槐树诅咒歌谣；（指向郭大槐散布谣言）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">一本郭氏祖训； （证明老槐树确实是穿越时空的介质）④</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">一张村里人的名单； （指向郭大槐调查赤脚医生和知青）⑤ 郭爷爷的遗嘱，树在人在，树死人亡； （指向郭大槐杀机）6 钱老板</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">①写给阿有的信件； （指向钱老板的真实身份）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">② 每年给老槐树汇款的记录； （指向钱老板与老槐树村有关系）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">③一本石头的手札，由于钱老板借住在石头家中，因此石头的手札也在钱</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">老板处找到。（证明终石明即是崔小九，以及老槐树确实能令人穿越时空）④郝大爷送的一本书； （指向吴富贵在模仿郝大爷的字迹）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">⑤一张旧报纸上面记载着郝某被评为长春第一汽车制造厂标兵劳模的光荣事迹； （指向钱老板姓郝，也指向钱老板是个左撇子）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">7办公室</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">①修路经费申请表；（与下条线索关联）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">②工程队来信；（与上条线索关联，指向吴富贵想要贪污修路经费）③字帖；（指向吴富贵在模仿钱老板的爹郝大爷的笔迹）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">④小石头失踪报告；（指向小石头失踪时间为1959年与癌疫联系在一起）⑤写给大酒商的信; (指向吴富贵想要独占槐花酿)</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">⑤吴富贵的防疫英雄证书； （指向当年崔家三口之死和赤脚医生的杀机）8打谷场</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">①遗落的弹弓； （指向知青）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">②中间有小洞的木板；（指向知青的，小孔成像制造鬼影）③演讲稿上的白色粉末； （指向赤脚医生）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">④尸体嘴里塞着赵香兰的手帕，身上捆着绳子；（指向赵香兰去过打谷场以</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">及吴富贵是死前被人拖下井中）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">⑤尸体脸上有淤肿（右脸），后脑勺有伤口，指甲留有淤泥；（右脸淤肿说</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">明施暴者用的是左手，指向左撇子钱老板；后脑勺的伤口指向知青和弹弓；指甲淤泥指向死前挣扎）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">⑤井边路有些奇怪； （指向死者死前挣扎过）其他证据：</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">①赤脚医生剧本中郝大爷给崔家送饭染病而亡；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">②秀琴剧本里郝大爷是被吴富贵逼迫去送饭;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">③秀琴剧本里和水儿同一天去赤脚医生处看病，并且大打出手（拿错了药）；④秀琴剧本里提到当年和吴富贵一起纵火的人有周琦、季礼全、刘金山、牛二民。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">⑤知青剧本里提到哥哥石头善良正直，联系崔家大火过后下葬的三具尸骨，推出小石头代替崔小九葬身火海；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">®知青剧本中提到拿弹弓打吴富贵时听到吴富贵威胁寡妇要将其的秘密公开，指向寡妇杀害傻柱；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">②郭大槐剧本中提到知青与水儿七天前风蚀崖相会；杀人动机说明：</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">赤脚医生：十年前崔家大火；知青：水儿之死；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">秀琴：①丈夫出轨；②想拿到300元抚恤金；赵香兰：①被欺负；②被威胁；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">郭大槐：①吴富贵要砍掉其赖以生存的老槐树；②吴富贵偷了其祖传秘方；钱老板：吴富贵为了金钱害死其父亲郝大爷；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">问题答案:</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">1死者是谁（需回答姓名，年龄）45岁的郝有钱</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2死者为什么会在这里</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">1979年来祭拜父亲，不小心穿越到了1969年的老槐树村3死者砍树的真正原因是什么</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">阻止陨石击中村落</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">4佟石明是谁</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">崔小九</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">5寡妇和秀琴八岁时救起的女婴分别是谁</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">都是赵香兰</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">6老槐树村为什么会消失</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; cursor: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.3px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">因为被陨石砸进了平行时空</p><p>&ZeroWidthSpace;<br></p></body>`